<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
	
	<p n="1">Prosperity! Fortune!</p>
	
	<p n="2-3">Eighteenth year of Kampavarmaṉ.<note>Sanskrit Kampavarman.</note></p>
	
	<p n="4-12">
		<supplied reason="subaudible">There are</supplied> ten <foreign>kaḻañcu</foreign>s of gold that
		...,
		the Brahmin <supplied reason="subaudible">spouse</supplied> of
		...
		gave for a perpetual lamp for the glorious Subrahmaṇya ...
	</p>
	
	<p n="12-16">
		We, the members of the assembly, have become those who will ...
	</p>
			
